{"type": "article", "id": 28475, "title": "可以泡咖啡的闹钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-21T06:46:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702161656urMeZn3wSvNaotyK.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>想要一起床就能喝到咖啡或者茶？这台名为 Barisieur 的机器可以满足你的梦想。除了冲调热饮之外，它的底座还是一个闹钟，特意采用加热水时让钢球震动的声音作为闹铃声，很有特色。事先把咖啡粉或者茶叶放进机器的小抽屉内，设置好时间，Barisieur 就会为你煮好热饮。Barisieur 时尚的造型不管是放在床头柜上还是办公区域都很合适，底座还配有一个 USB 充电口可以为手机充电。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/393281213/the-barisieur-designer-coffee-and-tea-alarm-clock\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 230 英镑。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021616488Jwe9HacAmoN7it4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.56259205\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021616493KprXsloWkunGv5P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161650S6iQeYEgj3OdVT9m.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021616508SjZiUx3bpHeFh1Y.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}